author: Red Means Recording
description:
Download for free here: https://jjbbllkk.itch.io/chorus-somnia
Check out the vocal library here: https://www.feveraudio.com/

Chorus Somnia is a release of 4 completely free and free-to-use experimental cinematic vocal pieces made with the Fever Dreams Kontakt library by Fever Audio. Inspired by the work of Cristobal Tapia de Veer and A24 horror movie trailer music.
title: Vocal Instruments Are Fun
